				"id": "",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Grupp</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Substanser</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Opiater och </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>opioider<sup>a</sup></strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Morfin, heroin, r&aring;opium,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">kodein, metadon, petidin,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">etylmorfin, ketobemidon,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">buprenorfin, dextropropoxifen, <br />tramadol, fentanyl</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue Ultra Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sedativa/hypnotika</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Alkohol</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Etanol, metanol, kloralhydrat</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Barbiturater</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Metohexital, pentotal, fenemal, <br />meprobamat</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Bensodiazepiner</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Diazepam, klordiazepoxid,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">klonazepam, lorazepam,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">alprazolam, midazolam,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">oxazepam, nitrazepam,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">flunitrazepam, triazolam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&Ouml;vriga</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Zolpidem, zopiklon, zaleplon, <br />klometiazol</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. Central</span><strong>stimulantia</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Amfetamin, metamfetamin,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">fenmetrazin, metylfenidat,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">ecstasy (MDMA), khat (quat,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">qat, tschat, miraa)</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Kokain</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kokain, crack, \"free-base\"</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. Cannabinoider</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Hasch, marijuana</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. Halluci</span><strong>nogener</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">LSD, meskalin, psilocybin</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" class=\"footNotes\">\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_13\"><strong></strong>\"Opiater\" refererar till narkotiska alkaloider utvunna ur\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">opium (till exempel morfin och kodein) eller derivat av dessa alka-</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">loider (till exempel heroin). \"Opioider\" refererar till medel som inte</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&auml;r opiater, men har liknande farmakologiska effekter (till exempel</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">syntetiska substanser som ketobemidon, eller endogena opioida <br />peptider som enkefalin).</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
