				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>L&auml;kemedel</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>T<sub>max</sub><sup>b</sup> (timmar)</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Halveringstid<sup>c</sup></strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Dos ekvivalent med</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>5 mg diazepam (mg)</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Klonazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1&ndash;4</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">L&aring;ng</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">0,25</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Triazolam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1,7</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">0,25</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Alprazolam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">0,5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Flunitrazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">0,5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Lorazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1&ndash;2</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1,0</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Nitrazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1,5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">2,5</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Diazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">1</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">L&aring;ng</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">5,0</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Oxazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">2</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Kort</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">15,0</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"4\" class=\"footNotes\">\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_19\">Missbrukspotentialen &auml;r fr&auml;mst relaterad till tv&aring; variabler: affiniteten f&ouml;r receptorn, respektive snabbheten i tillslaget. H&ouml;gre affinitet motsvaras (f&ouml;r en full agonist) av en l&auml;gre ekvipotent dos, h&auml;r angiven i dosekvivalenter diazepam.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_20\">Tid till tillslag anges h&auml;r som antal timmar till maximal plasmakoncentration.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_21\">Ackumulationsrisken &auml;r relaterad till eliminationshalveringstiden, h&auml;r grovt klassificerad som l&aring;ng (&gt;&nbsp;24 timmar) respektive kort (&lt;&nbsp;24 timmar).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
